Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara...would you like\Na Moscow Mule?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz, I have juice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz, thank your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.\NHe'll get used to me eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The antique business I just started\Nwill also take off eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was just so sudden for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly get to live in\Nsuch a wonderful home,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and my sweet husband\Nmakes delicious cocktails for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, did you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The house next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I get the feeling\Nthat someone is watching us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,from the window of the second floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That house is empty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mrs. Daughtry,\Nfrom across the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,told me something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty years ago, a couple\Nwas brutally murdered next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that ghosts have\Nbeen seen in that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that\Nyou believe that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... No, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be good for\Njust the three of us to go out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We probably don't need a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Fritz will probably warm up\Nto you faster that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective, what are the results\Nof the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, regarding Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are chasing him as\Na suspect in the Fortner murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But they couldn't find out\Nanything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When Dr. Tenma was\Nsummoned by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,he said that a boy whose life\Nhe saved ten years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,had murdered the director of\NEisler Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and three others, and had run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy's name is Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, the adult Johan murdered\Nsomeone right in front of Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Nina Fortner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the daughter of\Nthe murdered couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Her whereabouts are also unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as for Mr. Mesner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed him to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He was brutally stabbed\Ntwo months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The official line is that\Nhe was killed in a drug dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesner was my partner\Nwhen I was a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mesner was dismissed from\Nthe police for narcotics possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A man called "The Baby" saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the boss of\Nan extreme right-wing organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that\Nhave to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Last winter, a group of people tried to\Nset fire to Frankfurt's Turkish district.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There are rumors that\N"The Baby" was the ringleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,An Asian man stopped the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing. Rumor has it that\N"The Baby" started the fires
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to welcome a certain young man\Nto his organization as it's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the name of the boy\Nwho Tenma saved ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The youth who "The Baby" tried to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:06:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,install as his organization's leader\Nis also called Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're coming at me that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Roberto, my life is like\Nthis chess piece, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always a loser in life.\NUntil I got that phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a detective who sold\Nconfiscated drugs on the black market
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,with my partner Mesner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The caller knew everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We just had to kill a certain couple\Nif we wanted him to keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be saved if we killed\Nthe Fortners in Heidelberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one more person\Nthat night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A newspaper journalist, or something,\Nwas also in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesner and I\Nkilled all three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we were given\Na large sum of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I left the police force,\NI was picked up by the Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was even given a good post.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The money I made\Nwas easily laundered...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you met your wife\Nand went straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I get out of\Nthat organization so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who made that phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave me\Nthat large sum of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's controlling my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, I'm grateful to you\Nfor protecting me all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could you take back\Nthat last move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something that I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy me a toy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye to your father, Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All he can think about are toys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, were there any calls\Nfrom the detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He should have come by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, it's the detective!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the daughter of the Fortners,\Nthe couple you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bodyguard, Roberto,\Nwas the one who killed that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw everything from\Nthe house next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto is a friend I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to get revenge on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You have someone you can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mr. Muller?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Muller?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive out of here, quickly!\NNow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been watching me\Nall this time from
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the house next door, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you planning to\Ndo with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you from\Nthe bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was forced to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he'd reveal that I was\Nselling narcotics on the black market
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,if I didn't kill your parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So...I had to team up with Mesner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You...had to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They were wonderful people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They were really wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother and father loved me\Nfrom the bottom of their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even their real daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother and father...\Nreally...really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop–!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But they were killed by\Na scoundrel like you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara... Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara... Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara... Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what it's like to be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz called me Dad for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got things I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara... Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf...every morning\Nat 8:30 at that cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When I joined the Syndicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,my boss ordered me to pose as\Na businessman each morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning, a mother\Npassed by with her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my only connection\Nwith normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-Hey 'morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you ask\Nyour detective to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Find you and Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And find information about Mesner,\Nmy former police partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mesner is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hired an investigator\Nwho was familiar with the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a call from\Nthe detective last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things are getting strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,– Strange?\N{\i1}– Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Mesner was\Nalready a junkie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wasn't someone who would get\Nin a dispute with the Syndicate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more thing. The culprit wasn't\Nfrom Frankfurt's organization,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but from Düsseldorf...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well...I'll tell you\Nthe rest of the details in person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A draft of the report...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"The culprit of...the Mesner case."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is...Roberto?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to return my bag.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roberto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your wife and Fritz\Nare with me right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What did you say? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Put my wife on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should come back quickly\Nto your "happy home"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you lend me a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only use\Nthat gun at short range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only four shots...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good enough.\NI was once a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die, I can't tell\Nthe police the truth...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cover you from\Nthe empty house next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, look, it's a fishing pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He absolutely insisted on\Ngoing fishing with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where's Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of his friends from\Nthe security company have come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like something happened\Nwhile we were out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Nobody was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Roberto, Michael's come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. A window was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the neighborhood kids\Nwas probably causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where's the body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to\Nthe detective's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto! Who...Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife and Fritz are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, don't\Nmake things complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Nothing happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was a peaceful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It will continue to be peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a beautiful girl, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... What did you do to Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We are treating her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She is an important guest\Nto a certain individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The name of that young man\Nis also Johan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan! Johan! Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Johan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to live a happy life\Nwith your wife and Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We go our separate ways today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to Nina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to\Ntake me fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, if the weather's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer see ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You look a lot like Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When can I meet Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cooperating because you said\Nthat you would let me meet Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, he wants to\Nmeet you as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's living happily in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Munich?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's truly a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... All that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an ex-detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...I promised Fritz\Nthat I would go fishing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the weather's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will be...
